creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of Yesterdays by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; Sonia; clover3lee; Rune; Andree-Ann Granger; Newgatenovelist; Jude; Joe Brenneman; Shakira Searle; Kathleen Flanary; Nancy; Adele Parry; Emerie; Kathleen Moore
This is a volume of early poetry by Ella Wheeler Wilcox. As much of Ella Wheeler Wilcox's poetry, this volume also conveys a number of different emotions in the different poems. Ms Wilcox herself suggests the alternative title "Ghosts of old dreams" for this volume. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

title: Yesterdays
